<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Michael&#32;had&#32;been&#32;on&#32;the&#32;road&#32;for&#32;hours.&#32;His&#32;tires&#32;had&#32;now&#32;worn&#32;from&#32;the&#32;stress&#32;of&#32;gravel&#32;pits&#32;and&#32;broken&#32;tarmac.&#32;The&#32;light&#32;from&#32;the&#32;moon&#32;barely&#32;made&#32;a&#32;dent&#32;in&#32;the&#32;environment&#32;around&#32;him,&#32;the...</span><br />
